---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import ppeWorker from '../assets/Trabajador_con_EPP_202603190949.png';
---

<!-- SECTION 4: GESTIÓN SST Y CUMPLIMIENTO NORMATIVO -->
<section id='sst' class='relative bg-iaas-bg overflow-hidden'>
  <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-10 sm:py-14 lg:py-16'>
    <!-- Main Grid -->
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16'>
      <!-- Left Column: Content -->
      <div>
        <!-- Title -->
        <h2
          class='text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[2.8rem] font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900 mb-4'
        >
          Gestión <span class='text-iaas-blue'>SST</span> y Cumplimiento
          <span class='text-iaas-blue'>Normativo</span>
        </h2>

        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <div class='bg-white border-l-4 border-iaas-blue rounded-r-lg p-4 mb-8'>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            Garantizamos entornos laborales seguros y cumplimiento legal bajo la <strong class='text-gray-900'>Ley N° 29783</strong>, y las diferentes normativas sectoriales así como estándares ISO.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Two columns: Sistemas de Gestión + Vigilancia Médica -->
        <div class='grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8'>
          <!-- Sistemas de Gestión -->
          <div>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-4'>
              <div
                class='w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue flex items-center justify-center'
              >
                <svg
                  class='w-4 h-4 text-white'
                  fill='none'
                  viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                  stroke='currentColor'
                  stroke-width='2'
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap='round'
                    stroke-linejoin='round'
                    d='M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z'
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class='text-sm font-bold text-gray-900'>
                Sistemas de Gestión
              </h3>
            </div>
            <ul class='space-y-2.5 text-[12px] text-iaas-gray'>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Implementación ISO 45001
              </li>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Consultoría para Certificación ISO 45001
              </li>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Homologación de proveedores
              </li>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Auditorías
              </li>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Supervisión de trabajos de alto riesgo
              </li>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Gestión de contratistas
              </li>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Asesoría legal SST
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Vigilancia Médica -->
          <div>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-4'>
              <div
                class='w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue flex items-center justify-center'
              >
                <svg
                  class='w-4 h-4 text-white'
                  fill='none'
                  viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                  stroke='currentColor'
                  stroke-width='2'
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap='round'
                    stroke-linejoin='round'
                    d='M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z'
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class='text-sm font-bold text-gray-900'>Servicios Adicionales</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class='space-y-2.5 text-[12px] text-iaas-gray'>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Capacitación especializada: trabajos en altura, espacios confinados, eléctricos, izaje de cargas
              </li>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Inspecciones técnicas de seguridad en edificaciones (ITSE)
              </li>
              <li class='flex items-start gap-2'>
                <span class='w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-iaas-blue mt-1.5 shrink-0'
                ></span>
                Seguridad en el diseño: medidas de protección desde etapas iniciales del proyecto
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Monitoreos Ocupacionales -->
        <div class='bg-iaas-dark rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6'>
          <h4
            class='text-xs font-bold text-white tracking-wider uppercase mb-4'
          >
            Monitoreos Ocupacionales
          </h4>
          <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-2.5'>
            <span
              class='inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-[11px] text-white/90'
            >
              <svg
                class='w-3 h-3'
                fill='none'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap='round'
                  stroke-linejoin='round'
                  d='M15.536 8.464a5 5 0 010 7.072M12 6a7.975 7.975 0 015.657 2.343M12 6a7.975 7.975 0 00-5.657 2.343m11.314 0A7.975 7.975 0 0120 12m-8-6a7.975 7.975 0 00-5.657 2.343M4 12a7.975 7.975 0 002.343 5.657'
                ></path></svg
              >
              Ruido
            </span>
            <span
              class='inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-[11px] text-white/90'
            >
              <svg
                class='w-3 h-3'
                fill='none'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap='round'
                  stroke-linejoin='round'
                  d='M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z'
                ></path></svg
              >
              Iluminación
            </span>
            <span
              class='inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-[11px] text-white/90'
            >
              <svg
                class='w-3 h-3'
                fill='none'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap='round'
                  stroke-linejoin='round'
                  d='M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707'
                ></path></svg
              >
              Estrés Térmico
            </span>
            <span
              class='inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-[11px] text-white/90'
            >
              <svg
                class='w-3 h-3'
                fill='none'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap='round'
                  stroke-linejoin='round'
                  d='M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z'
                ></path></svg
              >
              Calidad de Aire
            </span>
            <span
              class='inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-[11px] text-white/90'
            >
              <svg
                class='w-3 h-3'
                fill='none'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap='round'
                  stroke-linejoin='round'
                  d='M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z'
                ></path></svg
              >
              Agentes Químicos
            </span>
            <span
              class='inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-[11px] text-white/90'
            >
              <svg
                class='w-3 h-3'
                fill='none'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap='round'
                  stroke-linejoin='round'
                  d='M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z'
                ></path></svg
              >
              Ergonómicos
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Vertical image + EPP badges + Culture -->
      <div class='flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6'>
        <!-- Vertical worker image -->
        <div class='relative w-full max-w-md px-2 sm:px-6 py-4 sm:py-6'>
          <div class='relative mx-auto w-64 sm:w-72 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_50px_-18px_rgba(10,77,140,0.35)] border border-white/70'>
            <div class='aspect-3/4 sm:aspect-4/5 bg-white'>
              <Picture
                src={ppeWorker}
                formats={['avif', 'webp']}
                alt='Trabajador con Equipo de Protección Personal completo'
                class='w-full h-full object-cover object-top'
                widths={[320, 480, 768]}
                sizes='(max-width: 640px) 320px, (max-width: 1024px) 480px, 768px'
                quality={80}
                loading='lazy'
              />
            </div>
            <div class='absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-iaas-dark/35 via-transparent to-transparent'></div>
            <div class='absolute top-4 left-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/95 px-3 py-1.5 shadow-md'>
              <span class='w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500'></span>
              <span class='text-[10px] font-bold text-iaas-dark tracking-wide uppercase'>EPP completo</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Protecciones alrededor de la imagen -->
          <div class='absolute top-0 left-0 sm:left-2 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-iaas-blue/15 px-2.5 py-2 shadow-md'>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-1.5'>
              <svg class='w-3.5 h-3.5 text-iaas-blue shrink-0' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'>
                <path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' d='M20.618 5.984A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z'></path>
              </svg>
              <span class='text-[10px] font-semibold text-iaas-gray'>Casco</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='absolute top-0 right-0 sm:right-2 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-iaas-blue/15 px-2.5 py-2 shadow-md'>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-1.5'>
              <svg class='w-3.5 h-3.5 text-iaas-blue shrink-0' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'>
                <path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' d='M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z'></path>
                <path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' d='M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z'></path>
              </svg>
              <span class='text-[10px] font-semibold text-iaas-gray'>Lentes</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='absolute top-1/2 left-0 sm:left-1 -translate-y-1/2 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-iaas-blue/15 px-2.5 py-2 shadow-md'>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-1.5'>
              <svg class='w-3.5 h-3.5 text-iaas-blue shrink-0' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'>
                <path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' d='M7 11.5V14m0-2.5v-6a1.5 1.5 0 113 0m-3 6a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0v2a7.5 7.5 0 0015 0v-5a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-6-3V11m0-5.5v-1a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v1m0 0V11m0-5.5a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v3m0 0V11'></path>
              </svg>
              <span class='text-[10px] font-semibold text-iaas-gray'>Guantes</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='absolute top-1/2 right-0 sm:right-1 -translate-y-1/2 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-iaas-blue/15 px-2.5 py-2 shadow-md'>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-1.5'>
              <svg class='w-3.5 h-3.5 text-iaas-blue shrink-0' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'>
                <path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' d='M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z'></path>
              </svg>
              <span class='text-[10px] font-semibold text-iaas-gray'>Chaleco</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-iaas-blue/15 px-2.5 py-2 shadow-md'>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-1.5'>
              <svg class='w-3.5 h-3.5 text-iaas-blue shrink-0' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'>
                <path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' d='M5 13l4 4L19 7'></path>
              </svg>
              <span class='text-[10px] font-semibold text-iaas-gray whitespace-nowrap'>Botas de seguridad</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cultura de Prevención -->
        <div class='w-full max-w-sm bg-white rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 text-center shadow-sm border border-gray-100'>
          <h4
            class='text-xs font-bold text-iaas-blue tracking-wider uppercase mb-3'
          >
            Cultura de Prevención
          </h4>
          <blockquote>
            <p class='text-sm text-iaas-gray italic leading-relaxed'>
              "La seguridad no es un gasto, es la inversión más valiosa de su
              organización."
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
